      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "say need to identify\na particular student from\na particular couse->\n\n\n-Student_id alone\nwouldnt be enough since\na student could enroll in \nmultiple courses\n\n\nthe same for courses as well\nsince there might be\nmultiple students \nenrolling in a single course",
